# Legacy DaKanjiDB parsers

This contains the legacy parsers of DaKanjiDB.
While these work, they are mostly not used in the current parsing process.
They are kept here for reference and potential future use, but they may not be maintained or updated.

This approach used an in-memory map to load the data somewhat efficiently.
But the memory is rising and the speed is decraesing the more dictionaries are imported.
Therefore, the V2 parsers have been built which are in `../staging_db/` 
